# KubeWise — Configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in your values.

## OpenRouter (for LLM-based analysis — optional in Phase 1)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

## Agent
KUBEWISE_DATA_DIR=/tmp/kubewise
KUBEWISE_ADDR=:8080
KUBEWISE_CONFIG_PATH=./config.yaml

## Prometheus
PROMETHEUS_ADDRESS=http://localhost:9090

## Scraping
SCRAPE_INTERVAL=30s
